    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【关于本作】<br> 打造你的梦想咖啡馆，并在桌面下方静静运行！<br> 即便不操作也能自动经营，不打扰你的日常工作。<br> 《遗忘周一咖啡馆》是一款可以像桌面小工具一样运行的放置型咖啡馆模拟经营游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过观众留言进行互动！<br> 在进行直播时，观众可以通过评论进入你的咖啡馆点单下单。支持 YouTube 与 Twitch 等平台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167540/extras/d85c9ff652971b4eb21d97c175a898c9.poster.avif?t=1769139933\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167540/extras/d85c9ff652971b4eb21d97c175a898c9.webm?t=1769139933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167540/extras/d85c9ff652971b4eb21d97c175a898c9.mp4?t=1769139933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以亲自打理咖啡馆，也可以交给员工自动运行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣员工后，即便离开电脑，他们也能为你打理好一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167540/extras/b7d084910ca278b20ff0e3b8dc32fb28.poster.avif?t=1769139933\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167540/extras/b7d084910ca278b20ff0e3b8dc32fb28.webm?t=1769139933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167540/extras/b7d084910ca278b20ff0e3b8dc32fb28.mp4?t=1769139933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然是一款 PC 游戏，但不会占据你的整个屏幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以一边工作，一边欣赏咖啡馆的成长和变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
